𝗪𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐭𝐞,𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐬.⁣
But on the other side we cling on to negativity as a survival technique .Additionally we also have “confirmation bias” which is that we seek to confirm what we already believe .This is why you are unconsciously seeking information that confirms what you believe deep down about yourself and the world .⁣
.⁣
You are in charge of what information you take in what you focus on , how do u react to it & what sort of life you want to live.you have the ability to change your life the way you want it to be ⁣
